{"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"- ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"void"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"selected"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"animated:"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:@T@BOOL","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"BOOL"},{"kind":"text","text":") "},{"kind":"internalParam","text":"animated"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"]}]},{"kind":"parameters","parameters":[{"name":"selected","content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"codeVoice","code":"YES"},{"text":" if the view should display itself as selected; ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"NO"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"if it should display itself as unselected.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]},{"name":"animated","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"code":"YES","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if the change in selection state is animated; ","type":"text"},{"code":"NO","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" if the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"change is immediate.","type":"text"}]}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"text":"Discussion","type":"heading","level":2,"anchor":"discussion"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"You should not call this method directly. A map view calls this method in","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"response to user interactions with the annotation. Subclasses may override this","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"method in order to customize the appearance of the view depending on its","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"selection state.","type":"text"}]},{"text":"Related examples","type":"heading","level":4,"anchor":"Related-examples"},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample"}]}]}]}]}],"kind":"symbol","metadata":{"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"externalID":"c:objc(cs)MLNAnnotationView(im)setSelected:animated:","role":"symbol","title":"setSelected:animated:","modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"fragments":[{"kind":"text","text":"- "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"setSelected:animated:"}],"symbolKind":"method","remoteSource":{"url":"https:\/\/github.com\/maplibre\/maplibre-native\/blob\/main\/platform\/ios\/src\/MLNAnnotationView.h#L230","fileName":"MLNAnnotationView.h"},"roleHeading":"Instance Method"},"sections":[],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"]]},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:"},"abstract":[{"text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation.","type":"text"}],"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView/setSelected:animated:":{"navigatorTitle":[{"text":"setSelected:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview\/setselected:animated:","kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"- ","kind":"text"},{"text":"setSelected:animated:","kind":"identifier"}],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Sets the selection state of the annotation view with an optional animation."}],"type":"topic","title":"setSelected:animated:","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView\/setSelected:animated:","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre","role":"collection","title":"MapLibre","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","role":"symbol","type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotationView":{"title":"MLNAnnotationView","role":"symbol","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotationview","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotationView"},{"type":"text","text":" class is responsible for marking a point annotation"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a view. Annotation views represent an annotation object, which is an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"object that corresponds to the "},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol. When an annotation’s"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"geographic coordinate is visible in the map view, the map view asks its"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"delegate to a corresponding annotation view. If an annotation view is created"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"with a reuse identifier, the map view may recycle the view when it goes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"offscreen."}],"kind":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotationView"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS/AnnotationViewExample":{"role":"article","kind":"article","abstract":[{"text":"Add a custom annotation view","type":"text"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre-Native-for-iOS\/AnnotationViewExample","type":"topic","title":"Custom Annotation View","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre-native-for-ios\/annotationviewexample"}}}